libs.content:
find_library(mmg2d_mmg2d_library
      names mmg2d
      hints ${mmg_dir}
      path_suffixes lib lib32 lib64)

find_library(mmgs_mmgs_library
      names mmgs
      hints ${mmg_dir}
      path_suffixes lib lib32 lib64)

find_library(mmg3d_mmg3d_library
      names mmg3d
      hints ${mmg_dir}
      path_suffixes lib lib32 lib64)

deps.context:
find_package(boost required components
    chrono
    date_time
    filesystem
    program_options
    system
    thread
    unit_test_framework
    )

libs.content:
find_library(
        fftw_lib
        names "fftw3"
        paths $env{fftwdir}
        path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
        no_default_path
        )

find_library(
        fftwf_lib
        names "fftw3f"
        paths $env{fftwdir}
        path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
        no_default_path
        )

find_library(
        fftwf_omp_lib
        names "fftw3f_omp"
        paths $env{fftwdir}
        path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
        no_default_path
        )
